---
title: Caribbean Style Bacon and BBQ Beans with Avocado, Cheese and Crispy Onions
description: Our Caribbean Style Bacon and BBQ Beans make the best of beans. Flavoured with jerk seasoning that contains paprika, cayenne, pimento and thyme, it's a hearty dish you didn't know you needed.
